{"product_id": "208480", "page": 7, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-10", "text": "In my honest opinion, I don\u2019t think ac3 was as imperfect as the community hyped it to be. Yes, it had it flaws but which Assassin Creed game didn\u2019t?\nPros\n1) Gameplay was very improved from the previous sequels.\n2) Better atmospheric\n3) Much improved Cinematic and graphics\n4) New navel and hunting mechanic\nCons\n1) Story till the mid game can get pretty fatigue\n2) Optimization issue\n3) Multiplayer servers are down\n\nHere are my ratings for the game.\n->Graphics (7.5/10)\n->Music (7/10)\n->Cinematic (8/10)\n->Story (7.5/10)\n->Content (9/10)\n->Controls (8.5/10)\n->Gameplay (9/10)\nOverall,I would give this game an 8/10 (80%) and Yes, I totally recommend this game.", "hours": 32.8, "username": "arshikayy", "products": 157, "early_access": false}
