{"product_id": "208480", "page": 7, "page_order": 9, "recommended": false, "date": "2018-01-09", "text": "Uplay mandatory, and a tedious protagonist added to the fact that AC is a series to which innovation seems unknown make it hard to recommend, UNLESS you absolutely love AC.\nDisappointingly, it comes with a strong start and an interesting protagonist, before changing the perspective to a different one altogether who I can barely remember anything of on account of how bland he is.\nMy conclusion on AC3 was that it was a game let down by Ubisoft's undeserved loyalty to the AC \"experience\", rather than doing something a bit different/unique in the AC universe.", "hours": 19.0, "username": "Moneybucks", "products": 189, "early_access": false}
