{"product_id": "208480", "page": 71, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-30", "text": "Overall I would say AC3 is quite good. A must try for an AC fan.\nPros:\n- Assassin trainees can do new skills\n- Big maps & many places\n- Improved free-running\n- Easy to kill enemies (Kinda)\n- Hunting is something new, and it's quite fun\n- Ability to assassinate while moving\n- Variety of weapons\n- Awesome killing animations\nCons:\n- Ending can't be chosen\n- Short & bad story\n- Not enough boss battles\n- Glitches are just hilarious\n\nIf I was able to play the game one more time, I guess I wouldn't. The story isn't exciting as AC2 although it has many new animations compared to AC2.", "hours": 35.4, "user_id": "76561198127188328", "username": "Havana", "products": 49, "early_access": false}
