{"product_id": "208480", "page": 73, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-11-26", "text": "Decided to try out the game again after a long break and the purchase of a much better equipped system.\nDownloaded game.\nHit play. Had to update Uplay (oh, right). Got everything updated.\nHit play again because the game wasn't running.\nClaimed it was already running.\nTried running from Uplay. Nothing.\nEnded the Uplay task and tried again from Steam.\nGame starts.\nI didn't see an option to turn off Vsync, could just be my mistake.\nStart a new game and get started.\nCrashes part way through the tutorial.\nClose Uplay for good and uninstall game.\nI'm good. I don't need that headache.", "hours": 8.6, "user_id": "76561197990986917", "username": "Womb Raider", "products": 471, "early_access": false}
