{"product_id": "208480", "page": 79, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-15", "text": "I love the entire Assassin's creed franchise and ive played and beaten almost every game in the series minus Unity. For me AC3 is probably my favorite AC game since during the time this came out I was learning about the American Revolution in school and it just fit well, ive beaten the game 3 time and i decided to go and play the game on PC but that was a bad mistake the port is poorly poorly optimized the game will run at a locked 60 then you get anywhere near populated areas like boston your fps just dies it honestly became unplayable for me. Beside the shawty PC port Assassin's creed 3 is a good game in the series and if you have a god teir PC itll probably run fine but for the lower end gamer wouldnt recommend the pc version just get the console version or something, unless your fine with some not so good performence", "hours": 1.4, "username": "Mama Raccoon", "products": 278, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "208480", "page": 79, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-14", "text": "AC3 \u00e9 e foi o game que fechou com chave de ouro a \"trilogia\". Ele \u00e9 completo, e assim como os demais, s\u00f3 adiciona e n\u00e3o remove nenhuma jogabilidade, tornando o jogo melhor e mais agradavel. A hist\u00f3ria n\u00e3o chega a altura da trilogia de Ezio, mas o personagem de uma certa maneira cativa pela ingenuidade, determina\u00e7\u00e3o e etnia. Um \u00edndio salvando os Patriotas contra os Britanicos pode ser lembrado por algumas obras cinematograficas e ser considerado clich\u00ea, contudo neste jogo encaixa perfeitamente. Al\u00e9m de enfrentar o preconceito, novas descobertas e a crueldade branca, ele deve ajudar a quem o machuca ao mesmo tempo. O jogo \u00e9 sensacional, as miss\u00f5es e as secundarias engrandecem o jogo e as dlc completam ainda mais a biblioteca de itens. A seasson pass, \u00e9 sem duvida uma maneira mais humilde de fechar o jogo por completo, mostrando ao presidente Washington o que aconteceria se ele ficasse com a ma\u00e7\u00e3 para transformas os EUA em uma pot\u00eancia, e ainda assim d\u00e1 um plot para a proxima aventura, pelo jeito que Connor esconde a ma\u00e7\u00e3... Falem o que quiser, o jogo pode ser repetitivo, mas ele sem d\u00favida me cativa e sua hist\u00f3ria sempre me prender\u00e1.", "hours": 50.5, "username": "Potato-dono", "products": 256, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "208480", "page": 79, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-14", "text": "Hi all. Today I will talk about the game Assassin's Creed III. I think the best game in the series that I review will try to tell you why. Let's start with the plot. The story I liked very much, it has everything for this game, great plot twists. Holes in the plot I was watching. Graphics/great Gameplay for games of that year, however, in one of the missions was a bug with the hair of Connor. The game also written a great soundtrack. The ending of the game is great, however, killed the main character of the series, that broke the series in my opinion. Overall the game is excellent and I advise everyone to play it. Besides the main missions, the game is available for many additional missions. Search for treasure, travel in the sea, to improve his estate, to liberate the city and to recruit new assassins. However, these missions are not so easy, but for them, you will get a good reward and enhance synchronization. This game changed the parkour, it was much better. My assessment of this game.\nThe plot - 10/10.\nGraphics/Gameplay - 8/10.\nSoundtrack - 10/10.\nParkour 9/10\n[RU]\u0412\u0441\u0435\u043c \u043f\u0440\u0438\u0432\u0435\u0442. \u0421\u0435\u0433\u043e\u0434\u043d\u044f \u044f \u0440\u0430\u0441\u0441\u043a\u0430\u0436\u0443 \u043e\u0431 \u0438\u0433\u0440\u0435 Assassin's Creed III. \u042f \u0441\u0447\u0438\u0442\u0430\u044e \u0438\u0433\u0440\u0443 \u043b\u0443\u0447\u0448\u0435\u0439 \u0432 \u0441\u0435\u0440\u0438\u0438, \u044f \u0432 \u043e\u0431\u0437\u043e\u0440\u0435 \u043f\u043e\u043f\u044b\u0442\u0430\u044e\u0441\u044c \u0440\u0430\u0441\u0441\u043a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0442\u044c \u043f\u043e\u0447\u0435\u043c\u0443. \u0418\u0442\u0430\u043a, \u043d\u0430\u0447\u043d\u0435\u043c \u0441 \u0441\u044e\u0436\u0435\u0442\u0430. \u0421\u044e\u0436\u0435\u0442 \u043c\u043d\u0435 \u043e\u0447\u0435\u043d\u044c \u0441\u0438\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e \u043