{"product_id": "208480", "page": 104, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-06-13", "text": "It's a pretty long game with decent gameplay, good graphics, decent music, decent story... but it doesn't really excel in any way. It took me multiple years to finish it because of how dull it is.\n+Perfectly functional\n+Good graphics, interesting setting\n+Furthers the plot of the AC Series\n-Dull gameplay, no surprises to an AC player\n-Story missions are poorly written, lots of \"why would [protagonist] do that\" or \"why would [bad guy] do that\" moments\n-Non-story missions are repetitive without much reward\n-Most of your tools don't come in handy. The useful ones like the Pistol and Bow are clunky and hard to use\n-You have no stealth tools (not even a crouch) but there are several stealth missions", "hours": 28.1, "username": "Johnathon Mushboy", "products": 341, "found_funny": 3, "early_access": false}
