{"product_id": "208480", "page": 118, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-03-11", "text": "This is a very expansive game, you can clearly see a lot of work and time went into it.\nAnd I'd say it's a work of art, it has a lot of these very small but significant details which add a lot of believability to the world and the characters, and you won't even see most of it if you're not paying close attention. It has a few bugs as well but nothing game breaking.\nOverall there's just so much to this game, it'd be a disservice not to recommend it.", "hours": 91.9, "username": "dyufozeon", "products": 267, "early_access": false}
