{"product_id": "208480", "page": 122, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-02-14", "text": "It was fun to play in the Civil War era, but that's pretty much all this game had going for it. It got old pretty fast, mostly due to the main assassin Connor. He was such a dull character. I honestly only finished it because I was interested in Desmond's story. I bought this on sale for cheap and it was about worth that.", "hours": 30.1, "username": "Xbobwilldie93X", "products": 337, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "208480", "page": 122, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-02-14", "text": "Even after replaying this game several times, it is still one of my favorite games, and definatley my favorite Assassin's Creed game. The story behind Connor, how he becomes an Assassin, and just what he does throughout the game is such an amazing story and incredibly exciting to see what happens and how everything unfolds. The gameplay is brilliant, the new features of parkour, hunting, and naval gameplay are amazing, the historical aspects are great, and the story is truly interesting and leads you to want to play all the way to the end. I absolutley recommend this game to anyone who enjoys Assassin's Creed games, or hell, even if you want to play a game that takes place, and uses, the events/people of the Revolutionary War.", "hours": 162.5, "user_id": "76561198063089365", "username": "Lewis", "products": 166, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "208480", "page": 122, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-02-14", "text": "At one point i overwrote my previous Uplay password. Why it didn't tell me that it was already used and said that i couldn't use it i have no \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 clue. I could not log into my Uplay account and thus could not play Assasins Creed III. I ended up having to cancel the purchase on the credit card i used resulting in a 2 month steam community ban. Another thing was that the credit card i used for buying it became an unaccepted method of purchase after the incident. Ubisoft needs to improve Uplay software or better yet, just get rid of it. Lord knows they wont do either.", "hours": 2.8, "username": "Bill Nye The Russian Spy", "products": 75, "early_access": false}
