{"product_id": "208480", "page": 190, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-14", "text": "Assaasin's Creed III represents the American Revolution and the final part of Desmond's journey... As such, it is a big ambitious game for the Assassin's Creed series... The game stars a native American named Connor who is characterized to be a freedom fighter for his nation and for the new American lands...\nThe gameplay is great aside from a few performance hiccups and Multiplayer is phenomenal. The story does take a dive later in the game but overall is a very fantastic. Make sure to do Homestead missions...\nHighly recommended!!!", "hours": 156.9, "username": "Tart-G", "products": 39, "early_access": false}
