{"product_id": "208480", "page": 199, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-05-26", "text": "For me the segments where you play as Desmond and Haytham Kenway were more interesting than playing with Connor. The character of Connor was lacking. Other then that the game still has tons of issues with glitches, bugs, dodgy camera.\nThe naval segments were really fun to play. Overall I think it's a missed opportunity for a great game.\nAlso credits you can not skip shouldn't be a thing at all.", "hours": 25.5, "username": "Wizarda", "products": 240, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "208480", "page": 199, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-05-25", "text": "I really liked Assassin's Creed 3. I am currently running a NVIDIA GeForce GTX 970 and there were a couple times I had to lower my graphic card settings so that I was actually able to do the quick time events. But other then that pain the overall game and story line was great. Great addition to the AC game line.", "hours": 17.6, "user_id": "76561198041287274", "username": "Dragoncuali", "products": 331, "early_access": false}
