{"product_id": "208480", "page": 242, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-08", "text": "Another good entry in the AC series. Story was, like other AC games, a conspiracy theorists dream. There wasn't a buildup of the fighting capabilities (which is good for those of us that played the previous games and get it already). The ship missions were a good break from the standard 3rd person parkour. The hunting and tree hopping were also a fun additions. Graphics weren't improved much between the Ezio games and this one; handling might have been a little bit less on-the-money here.", "hours": 67.0, "username": "SeanWilks", "products": 541, "early_access": false}
