{"product_id": "208480", "page": 246, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-30", "text": "Cra - zy !!!\nYou are immersed the english colonies of North America during the American War of Independence. The amerindian culture is really, really present in the game. To my opinion, because of that, the game is incredible. The keyboard controls have been greatly improved, they are almost flawless : less irritating that the preceding games. The storyline is great, the graphics are nice and the fights are dynamic. And a great new addition : naval missions.\nIn summary, really complete anf interesting game.", "hours": 115.1, "user_id": "76561198001584035", "username": "BobMammoth", "products": 314, "early_access": false}
