{"product_id": "208480", "page": 287, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-10-14", "text": "Just finished this game and I was sadly dissapointed.  It is by far the worst AC game in the franchise.  Here I'm just reviewing the single player.\nPros\n-Awesome setting, I love the Revolutionary war period.\n-Ship battles were freakin amazing.\nCons\n-The repetitiveness of AC continues in this game.  Not too much seemed fresh.\n-The story wasn't that good\n-Desmond's ending freakin sucked\n-Playing the game felt like a chore.\nOverall 6/10", "hours": 26.3, "user_id": "76561198024918178", "username": "WarZoneNoah", "products": 120, "early_access": false}
