{"product_id": "208480", "page": 298, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-09-28", "text": "Let me first point out that I\u2019m not exactly recommending this for the single player story. The improvements done in AC3 compared to it's predecessors is very satisfying thus making it a fresh experience. If you\u2019re patient enough to explore everything and pursue all the little tasks, AC3 could simply last you 60+ hours. Otherwise it\u2019s rather a short lived dull experience. However if you\u2019re a fan of the series and need to stay in the loop of the overall story do give it a shot. It\u2019s got a tiny bit of a twist.", "hours": 64.3, "username": "xearon.sklavesky", "products": 664, "early_access": false}
