{"product_id": "208480", "page": 301, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-09-13", "text": "I love the game, it's really great to see a different elementary school versioin of US history. I love how the game puts you into different perspectives of US history. The story line is really great and the game is quite fun. I can't wait until Unity comes out and we play in the French Revolution.\nThe Horse controls are very frustrating and the damn horse doesn't move--it keeps getting stuck in areas; so it's faster just to not use the damn thing!!!  There should be a way to \"TURN OFF\" the parkour. I feel like i'm playing spiderman with this guy...", "hours": 96.7, "username": "Manray", "products": 56, "early_access": false}
