{"product_id": "208480", "page": 303, "page_order": 8, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-09-07", "text": "After playing the first few Assassin's Creeds, I decided to buy this guy. So far, I have been very disappointed. The story line seems \"meh\" and doesn't pull me in. There are several individuals you want to assassinate. It seems like rather than developing a story, they throw in historical events in America's history. What you're left with is something that feels disjointed and frankly just boring. Rather than wanting to \"turn the next page\" or play another hour, you want to just hurry up and get it over with. For this, I give it a thumbs down.", "hours": 59.5, "user_id": "76561198013243880", "username": "ElektronJohn", "products": 45, "early_access": false}
