{"product_id": "208480", "page": 316, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-07-22", "text": "While I like the Assassin's Creed franchise, the games have been steadily declining in quality since the inclusion of multiplayer in Assassin's Creed: Brotherhood. This one is no exception. While I didn't think this game could be worse than \"Revelations\", it somehow managed it. The game is clunky to control, with Connor not doing what you want him to around a third of the time, the story is both unbelievable (in the bad way) and uninteresting, and bugs somehow still run rampant a year after its release. Its only redeeming features were the homestead missions and the naval combat system. Not sure if I will play Black Flag after this one. 3/10", "hours": 101.9, "username": "Togii", "products": 282, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "208480", "page": 316, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-07-21", "text": "When I first started playing this game I thought the keyboard controls were horrendous and progressing through the story was confusing at best. Since I've gotten back into the game, I've progressed to the point where I'm now playing as Connor. I've also switched over to using a controller as it's not as horrendous to use, but still bad.\nI'm finding that if I do the side missions along with the main story, that Connor is actually a good guy, his father is a\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665and seemed to switch sides, and both the redcoats and Patriots need to be put down for good. Too bad the natives didn't have enough power to get rid of these loser Europeans.\nThis Assassin's Creed is good if you like Native American culture, and if you want to know something about how the USA got started. While the game has taken liberties with the real history, for the most part it is fairly accurate to say that NA, blacks and any other people that weren't white were treated terribly. Both voice actors for Connor and his mother are actual Native Americans.", "hours": 110.3, "username": "untmdsprt", "products": 101, "early_access": false}
