{"product_id": "208480", "page": 327, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-06-30", "text": "Please. Get. Rid. Of. Uplay.\nI've played for dozens of hours already, but for some inexplicable reason I can't log into Uplay anymore and the account seems to have lost synchronisation of my Steam purchase. Buyer beware! As a result, I do not recommend buying this game.\nAs for the game, it's good. It's bigger and it's better. Even when the combat is still a bit weak and too easy for more experienced gamers. It has also become rather weak when it comes to stealth play. Do not expect a Thief (or Sniper Elite III)  level of stealth gameplay here, it's not really there.", "hours": 24.0, "username": "Chan-Tzu Ti", "products": 392, "early_access": false}
