{"product_id": "208480", "page": 329, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-29", "text": "This game is great!\nI used to play it every day (it was a pirate copy), then i decided to buy license to enjoy the multiplayer, and now i cant even open it. It only shows me the main screen and descrirtion, then it stops responding and closes\nCan someone help me with this?", "hours": 131.8, "username": "Paulsader", "products": 25, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "208480", "page": 329, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-29", "text": "The minigames in this game are pieces of\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 Wonky movement, glitchy executions, absolute worst \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing lockpicking controls EVER for PC, and you have a game that is far and away the worst AC I've ever played.\nNot to mention for some reason the lip syncing looks WORSE than it did in revelations.\nThere needs to be a \"this is an okay core game but an utter disappointment to the series\" rating.\nI'd still recommend anyone that plays AC to play it, but prepare for disappointment.", "hours": 45.9, "username": "Panda", "products": 334, "early_access": false}
