{"product_id": "208480", "page": 371, "page_order": 1, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-02-25", "text": "Gotta say, this is the one bad game I've ever played by Ubisoft. It seems like they decided to get rid of all the parts of Assassins Creed that I enjoy, what with a confusing fast travel system, a terrible port for pc and an obvious lack of effort into the weapons and mission hubs. There are no side quests, there are very limited weapons, the missions are repetitive and boring, and Connor himself isn't very likeable. No character development whatsoever, Connor is supposed to be a calm, patient person who doesn't like to kill. But his brutal combat skills contradict that fact. Also, Ubisoft advertised the game as centered around Connor as an assassin. Not until sequence 4 do you actually get to play as Connor, and you have to wait another sequence until he is an actual assassin. Altogether a disappointment to the AC series, although I believe they made up for it with Black Flag, which is the best AC game in my opinion.", "hours": 23.0, "username": "Aldephin", "products": 84, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "208480", "page": 371, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-25", "text": "A natural continuation of the Assassin's Creed series, nice sidequests and improved game mechanics from the other series. Graphics and sound does not disappoint even though they don't stand out on my quad core machine with a good ol GTX460.\nGood story as always, and many more sidequests than before. You can build your little empire if you so wish, which adds to the depth of the game and made me put in 80+ hours....but it is STILL to easy to just slaughter the entire defences of a city and take on 25 soldiers by yourself. Would like a harder game mode where you actually would HAVE TO run and hide instead of just countering all the attacks and kill every soldier in sight.\n8/10 Good entertainment! If you liked the other Assassin's Creed games this one is definitely something to consider, even more so if it is on sale.", "hours": 80.3, "username": "SwanT", "products": 100, "early_access": false}
