{"product_id": "208480", "page": 376, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-02-16", "text": "Assassin's Creed III is yet another Assassin's Creed rehash, only this one was advertised as being \"Completely different\", featuring \"All new mechanics\", which included triangles over opponents heads that flashed when you were going to be attacked. (Also completely missable naval battle minigames.)\nThe story is simple, rushed, and full of simple, unlikable one dimensional characters.\nThis game is garbage. \"Assassin's Creed\" means nothing but a series of shameless money grabs now.", "hours": 23.3, "user_id": "76561198041928563", "username": "Real Red", "products": 152, "early_access": false}
