{"product_id": "208480", "page": 408, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-16", "text": "Great Fun! Nice graphics combined with great gameplay. Lots of stuff to do.\nAlso preferring Connor over Ezio as a character. Its good to get some change from that Italian accent :p\nI have completed AC Brotherhood & Revelations. This one ive played about 20% completion and already choosing this over both of previous.\nStory start is somewhat boring but when you get to play as Connor, the fun starts!\nTheres still few complains ive seen so far.\nCombat system is way different from previous games, but i got used to it pretty soon as i started.\nAlso some controls are different.\nHighly recommending if you liked previous Assassin's creed's!", "hours": 71.9, "username": "ToGe", "products": 122, "early_access": false}
