{"product_id": "208480", "page": 425, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-10-18", "text": "The PC version of Assassin's Creed III has been injected with eye-popping enhancements that bring its compelling story to life. It's like personally participating in the American Revolution without the consequences of death. The ticket price of traveling back to the fascinating period of America's battle for independence, and the fictional story that Ubisoft Montpellier has layered within it, is just a copy of Assassin's Creed III and a high-end PC. Just remember that you'll have to leave your social life behind.", "hours": 18.3, "username": "Lactose", "products": 313, "early_access": false}
