{"product_id": "208480", "page": 442, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-02-17", "text": "Brings a new point of view for the franchise, not as Ezio.\nThe story is really strong and doesn't really rely on previous games, you encounter many famous people(George Washington etc.) which shaped America. The combat was also redone and significanly changed(nothing bad tho), the AI is quite dumb and there are bugs here and there, but overall, it's one of the best games in the Assassin's Creed franchise, if you are an action-adventure games fan, this one is definitely worth a try.", "hours": 119.4, "username": "Dawg", "products": 263, "early_access": false}
